'Credit Lite is a SaaS multi-branch co-operative credit union solution designed to help credit unions, co-operatives, and financial institutions manage accounts, loans, deposits, withdrawals, and online transactions efficiently.', NOW(), NOW()),

(2, 2, 'English---us', 'How does Credit Lite handle different account types?', 
'Credit Lite supports various account types, including savings accounts, fixed deposits, and member accounts, allowing institutions to customize financial services for their users.', NOW(), NOW()),

(3, 3, 'English---us', 'Can Credit Lite manage loans for members?', 
'Yes, Credit Lite features a loan management module that enables credit unions to issue loans, track repayments, set interest rates, and automate loan deductions from member accounts.', NOW(), NOW()),

(4, 4, 'English---us', 'Does Credit Lite have a member portal?', 
'Yes, Credit Lite provides a self-service member portal where members can check their balances, apply for loans, view transactions, and manage their financial activities online.', NOW(), NOW()),

(5, 5, 'English---us', 'How does Credit Lite handle deposits and withdrawals?', 
'Credit Lite allows credit unions to process member deposits and withdrawals securely, track transactions, and generate real-time financial reports.', NOW(), NOW()),

(6, 6, 'English---us', 'Can I integrate Credit Lite with online payment gateways?', 
'Yes, Credit Lite supports online payment gateway integrations, enabling members to deposit funds, repay loans, and withdraw money using digital payment methods.', NOW(), NOW()),

(7, 7, 'English---us', 'Is Credit Lite suitable for multi-branch credit unions?', 
'Absolutely! Credit Lite is designed to support multi-branch operations, allowing administrators to manage multiple branches from a single system while maintaining separate financial records.', NOW(), NOW()),

(8, 8, 'English---us', 'How secure is the data in Credit Lite?', 
'Credit Lite ensures data security with advanced encryption, regular backups, and secure cloud storage, protecting sensitive financial and member information.', NOW(), NOW()),

(9, 9, 'English---us', 'Can I integrate Credit Lite with third-party software?', 
'Yes, Credit Lite allows integration with accounting tools, banking systems, and other financial software to enhance operational efficiency.', NOW(), NOW()),

(10, 10, 'English---us', 'How do I get started with Credit Lite?', 
'Simply sign up for Credit Lite, choose a plan that suits your organization’s needs, and start managing your co-operative credit union operations seamlessly.', NOW(), NOW());


